The paper deals with recommending deep learning models for image datasets, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also discusses unsupervised learning (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural networks (cs.NE) in the context of the proposed approach.
